{"tid":1964063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"21歲仔墮貸款騙局　損失6萬元","createTime":"2020-04-08T14:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T15:21:38.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6abb688ea4ac5c59b63ceae57af315e617668f22","tid":1964063,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oynqvZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoynqvZV.jpg&h=c33b0f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(8日)下午2時許，警方接獲一名姓葉(21歲)男子報案，指經朋友認識一名自稱從事財務中介的男子，聲稱可協助自己向財務公司貸款約60萬元，但要先繳付約6萬元的保證金，葉男不虞有詐，遂按指示向該名男子繳交現金，惟其後向有關財務公司查證時，卻發現並無有關借貸紀錄，亦同時與對方失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n葉與家人商量後懷疑受騙，於是報案，警方經初步調查，案件列以欺騙手段取得財產，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200408/mobile/bkn-20200408203851417-0408_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200408%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200408203851417-0408_00822_001.html&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=373f76d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200408/mobile/bkn-20200408203851417-0408_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f9fdba462565efe34a3d7c72613e1977d3d44936","tid":1964063,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"咪比錢中介呢句口號賣咗廣告咁多年都中招？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b8d25dbeed113c803718e3ef85ba602dde0e8","tid":1964063,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"聲稱可協助自己向財務公司貸款約60萬元，但要先繳付約6萬元的保證金<br />\n<br />\n等同以前話咩請人返工 但要比幾千蚊公司先一樣<br />\n年年都有呢班死蠢"},{"pid":"befd9cd080dc4958f64543a60ceb2c97a713b4be","tid":1964063,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"21歲 有6萬 但又要借60萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706464c5ca4449844e0e7307e6002cf617c9380c"